Professional Life:
Despite the challenges of balancing work and family responsibilities, Olivia remains committed to her part-time retail job. She appreciates the steady income and the opportunity to interact with people, which provides a sense of purpose and social connection. Olivia is diligently looking for ways to improve her financial situation, such as pursuing additional job opportunities or exploring educational programs that could lead to better-paying positions.
